so we flash attention test can be passed by using the original attention layer code.
so lets baby step through each step of flash attention by replacing the original code with it.
that way its easier to isolate our mistake.

wow so these 2 are different:
> Sij = einsum(Qi, Kj, "... seq_q d_q, ... seq_k d_k -> ... seq_q seq_k") / math.sqrt(d_k)
> Sij = einsum(Qi, Kj, "... seq_q d, ... seq_k d -> ... seq_q seq_k") / math.sqrt(d_k)

okay we made it pass.
but what is strange is that we arnt following the paper exactly.
in fact, we found a difference between the algorithm in the paper and the algorithm in the assignment pdf.

